{"tid":1619732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[變身法律L] 《緊急情況規例條例》: 特首只可修訂成文法則","createTime":"2019-10-04T08:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:53:38.000Z","uid":110613,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc6821b3993fdbfd8eac71e3317e837b022c578","tid":1619732,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap241&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=cd967826\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKwsc1F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKwsc1F.png&h=3f13f851&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我睇黎睇去，只係得(g)可能岩用<br />\n<br />\n(g) 修訂任何成文法則，暫停實施任何成文法則，以及應用任何不論是否經修改的成文法則； <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>者係特首你剩係可以修訂/暫停/應用成文法則</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap1&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=1772f49a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1</a><br />\n成文法則定義<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYrDjLd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYrDjLd.png&h=b5337db5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而香港成文法則根本無禁蒙面法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以禁蒙面法唔包括係緊急法容許事項(a) - (n)入面</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n跪求法律巴絲引證"},{"pid":"0240b8d520d074a5c74d229791422eb0bb05471f","tid":1619732,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"23650098374aa4fc07c7ed9debd327f112129834","tid":1619732,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0