">所以禁蒙面法唔包括係緊急法容許事項(a) - (n)入面</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n跪求法律巴絲引證"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"咩呀 (1)呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />訂立合乎公眾利益的規例"},{"pid":"08e328ebfe5326525afee7e999af0a02b061167e","tid":1619732,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b6a61114a9ccf0336ce4d83954d840b7d9fa064","tid":1619732,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"在不損害第(1)款條文的一般性原則下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"佢意思係<br />\n特首係不損害第(1)款條文情況可以引用緊急法既情況<br />\n係唔包括今次立反蒙面法"},{"pid":"31d2161a2ceb16fd2e5fb140af8c2b31c9df26ab","tid":1619732,"uid":328913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46529c766bb972bbc77a713f6f884e064bda543c","tid":1619732,"uid":110613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b6a61114a9ccf0336ce4d83954d840b7d9fa064","tid":1619732,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"在不損害第(1)款條文的一般性原則下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"訂立規例的權力<br />\n(1)在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬緊急情況或危害公安的情況時，行政長官會同行政會議可訂立任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例。<br />\n<br />\n指既係佢在不損害公眾利益既原則下，該等規例可就下列事項作出規定：a - n"},{"pid":"073ba9aa4ef26dd32cce89f0a140cec5d78c36f2","tid":1619732,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e328ebfe5326525afee7e999af0a02b061167e","tid":1619732,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b6a61114a9ccf0336ce4d83954d840b7d9fa064","tid":1619732,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"在不損害第(1)款條文的一般性原則下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"佢意思係<br />\n特首係不損害第(1)款條文情況可以引用緊急法既情況<br />\n係唔包括今次立反蒙面法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"第(2)款條文 只係講左 (a) 至 (n) 各種事項<br />\n即係條法例無講可立蒙面法"},{"pid":"480cdeb4e57167b0fd8308dbb4049735b26e9ecb","tid":1619732,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"公眾利益有冇定義<br />\n1%人就行得？"},{"pid":"0f99d8e477a5f28f547ebfbe0778414b3b151414","tid":1619732,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24d46d377d50a14d24d071af5aa1226c9834121d","tid":1619732,"uid":198881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"480cdeb4e57167b0fd8308dbb4049735b26e9ecb","tid":1619732,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"公眾利益有冇定義<br />\n1%人就行得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"他認為合乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd10141ea5d5bb8ecc755729369db72b35ede6a8","tid":1619732,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:51:29.000Z","msg":"其實佢登左 Gazette 未?"},{"pid":"1875c3b93bb6b40eeb55b1ca2e2edd29b6e67bc5","tid":1619732,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"幾年前聽過<br />\n<br />\n特首唔同港督<br />\n特首係執行<br />\n唔可以有港督行緊急法既權力"},{"pid":"0ca2e7dea363037ca43dd4082627d0aa18998f5b","tid":1619732,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31d2161a2ceb16fd2e5fb140af8c2b31c9df26ab","tid":1619732,"uid":328913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"如果有(1)證明可以訂立咩例都得，(2)就無必要再例點啦？<br />\n同埋(1)既訂立指既係<br />\n(a)對刊物、文字、地圖、圖則、照片、通訊及通訊方法的檢查、管制及壓制；<br />\n(b)逮捕、羈留、驅逐及遞解離境；<br />\n(c)對香港的海港、港口及香港水域和對船隻移動的管制；<br />\n(d)陸路、航空或水上運輸，以及對運送人及東西的管制；<br />\n(e)貿易、出口、進口、生產及製造；<br />\n(f)對財產及其使用作出的撥配、管制、沒收及處置；<br />\n<br />\ng開始既動詞已經唔係訂立，只係權力"}]}